'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 48''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 48''',  was the 48th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''. It primarily reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 68|''Star Wars Insider'' 68]] and [[Star Wars Insider 69|''Star Wars Insider'' 69]].

